## Stack
# uni-app (Vue 3.4) + Express/PM2 + Laf Cloud (Sealos) + MongoDB

## Iron Rules
# 1. Layer order: Page → Component → Store → Service → Backend. No skipping.
# 2. All AI requests through proxy-ai.ts or ai.service.js
# 3. WeChat MP main package < 2MB
# 4. <script setup> Composition API only for new code
# 5. wot-design-uni components preferred
# 6. NEVER commit .env with real keys
# 7. NEVER skip requireAuth(ctx) on authenticated endpoints
# 8. NEVER call Pro/ prefix models on SiliconFlow DS keys

